# Cloudflare Pages headers — Phase 2 02-01, copied into public/ per Phase 4
# Plan 04-03 (Pitfall #8 + D-25 + 03-06 SUMMARY D-38). Astro auto-copies
# public/ → dist/ so dist/_headers ships byte-equivalent to the repo-root
# _headers file (which the legacy Python build path also relies on).
#
# /sw.js no-cache rule is the Phase 1 PMS-02 kill-switch invariant — without
# it the browser caches the SW script itself, defeating updates and stranding
# users on a stale SW indefinitely.
#
# CSP deferred to Phase 6 cutover (D-07). Edit via PR only.

/sw.js
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/_astro/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
